n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ShippingService\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常平均耗时增加至799ms，正常平均耗时196ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"EmailService\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常平均耗时增加至88222ms，正常平均耗时20617ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"PaymentService\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常平均耗时增加至75628ms，正常平均耗时13679ms\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "current_hypothesis": "The root cause is Node aiops-k8s-08 due to memory pressure, leading to service performance degradations in related pods, specifically cartservice-2 and productcatalogservice-2."}
